All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    Animal
    Animal class implements the methods in interface JungleSanctuary.
    AnimalTest
    Class for testing the all the functionality of Monkey class.
    CurrentLocStatus
    CurrentLocStatus is an enumeration which hold the 4 possible locations where a primate can be : ISOLATION, ENCLOSURE, TRANSFER, UNASSIGNED.
    EnclosureTest
    Class for testing the all the functionality of Enclosure class.
    FavoriteFood
    FavoriteFood is an enumeration which provides possible values for primate's favorite food : EGGS, FRUITS, INSECTS, LEAVES, NUTS, SEEDS, TREESAP.
    Housing
    Housing interface represents the housing units present in Jungle Sanctuary.
    HousingUnit
    Housing Unit class implements Housing interface.
    HousingUnitTest
    Class for testing the all the functionality of Housing Units class.
    IsolationTest
    Class for testing the all the functionality of Isolation class.
    JungleSanctuary
    JungleSanctuary represents a Sanctuary which houses multiple species and provides them shelter and medical support.
    Monkey
    Monkey class represents a single monkey with multiple attributes like name,age, weight, type of species, gender and housing details.
    MonkeyTest
    Class for testing the all the functionality of Monkey class.
    SanctuaryDriverClass
    Driver class to implement the functionality of the Jungle Sanctuary Project with default data.
    Sex
    Sex is an enumeration which provides possible values for primate's gender : MALE or FEMALE.
    Size
    Size is an enumeration which provides possible values for primate's size : SMALL, MEDIUM, LARGE.
    Species
    Species is an enumeration which provides possible values for primate's type DRILL, GUEREZA, HOWLER, MANGABEU, SAKI, SPIDER, SQUIRREL, TAMARIN.
